title: Beautiful Mill Valley 3 bedroom home (furnished)
posting_body: ['Fully furnished and equipped classic style Mill Valley mountain home.', "Located on one of Mill Valley's wider streets only 4 minutes up from town.", 'Completely rebuilt with a wonderful spacious kitchen (large island, marble countertops and stainless steel appliances) that opens to a dining room and also to a sitting room.', 'Separate main living room with deck looking out to the City.', 'Total of three bedrooms (two on the upper/main level one on the lower level - all with en suite bathrooms, plus an additional half bath on main level).', ' Utility room with washer/dryer and storage.', '  The lower level is bright and light with a further sitting area/play room and full kitchen and has its own fenced lawn and patio, (plus bedroom/ensuite bath as mentioned above).', 'Could be used as in-law suite or for live in help.', ' Parking is off street and there is room for two cars.', 'Perfect hopping off place for mountain biking and hiking on the endless trails of Mt Tam.', 'Large flat yard with lawns above and below the home.', 'Ideal for kids.', 'House is off the street up a private lane.', 'Small dogs and/or cats considered on a case by case basis.', 'Utilities including gas, electric, and garbage are not included.', ' TV/internet to be arranged by tenants.', 'Water included.', 'This is a no-smoking property.', 'Minimum one year lease preferred.', 'Cleaning services are not provided.', 'Available from early August 2022.', 'The home will be cleaned by professional cleaners in between tenancies.']
